tags.description: Chicane barrier: Challenging for tandems, trailers, wide or three wheel cycles.
tags.note: Path is a dead end at the east awaiting completion of a route under the railway.  At present there is no accces under the railway due to fencing at ground level.
There is no route east from this point as the railway viaduct is fenced off at ground level.
Public Footpath so no right of way for cycles or horses

tags.description: Dead end path but will be extended under the railway to link up with the National Cycle Route 12 to the east. Path will then become the official route 12.

tags.note: Cycle path can be used but is not complete so does not go through to the road beyond the railway. Local notice says expected to be created in 2024
Path being resurfaced and is currently closed.   20.9.24
